TITLE: Summer of Rage, Part I: Militant Pro-Abortion Radicals Flourish in Madison, Wisconsin; Violence ‘Meme'd’ on Twitter
SUMMARY: A far-left militant group with deep ties in Madison, Wisconsin, called Jane's Revenge has taken credit for violent attacks on pro-life pregnancy resource centers. The group has been allowed to spread their vigilantism on social media, seemingly in violation of the platforms' rules against promoting violence.
